ews/why-did-the-handwriting-in-this-248-year-old-notebook-look-familiar-it-turned-out-to-be-a-forgotten-mozart-manuscript-180989017/</link><description>1778年，作曲家在担任导师期间，在学生的帮助下创作了七首长笛和竖琴短曲。这个月，观众第一次听到演出的作品</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 17:17:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/why-did-the-handwriting-in-this-248-year-old-notebook-look-familiar-it-turned-out-to-be-a-forgotten-mozart-manuscript-180989017/</guid></item><item><title>1.2亿年前，这种奇怪的长有羽毛的恐龙可能像鼯鼠一样在树林间滑翔来捕食鸟类</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/this-strange-featured-dinosaur-may-have-glided-between-trees-like-a-flying-squirrel-to-hunt-birds-120-million-years-ago-180989011/</link><description>这种生物的化石提供了第一个证据，证明小盗龙生活在现在的中国西北部。它的发现也可能解开一个古老的谋杀之谜</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 16:04:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/this-strange-featured-dinosaur-may-have-glided-between-trees-like-a-flying-squirrel-to-hunt-birds-120-million-years-ago-180989011/</guid></item><item><title>灰鲸在旧金山湾遭到船只撞击。这种新的人工智能技术能拯救他们吗？</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/gray-whales-are-getting-struck-by-ships-in-san-francisco-bay-could-this-new-ai-powered-tech-save-them-180989009/</link><description>最近推出的系统包括两个热像仪，可以探测四英里外的灰鲸，让船只有足够的时间减速或改变航线，并避免撞上海洋哺乳动物</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/gray-whales-are-getting-struck-by-ships-in-san-francisco-bay-could-this-new-ai-powered-tech-save-them-180989009/</guid></item><item><title>维京人真的是“不文明”的野蛮人吗？丹麦发现的大型纺织品生产基地挑战了刻板印象</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/large-textile-production-site-discovered-in-denmark-challenges-the-stereotype-of-vikings-as-uncivilized-barbarians-180989014/</link><description>这个占地超过 100 万平方英尺的大型定居点可能可以追溯到公元 600 年至 950 年的铁器时代晚期或维京时代早期</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 21:31:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/large-textile-production-site-discovered-in-denmark-challenges-the-stereotype-of-vikings-as-uncivilized-barbarians-180989014/</guid></item><item><title>据报道，一幅被盗的毕加索在巴黎附近的一次缉毒行动中刚刚出现，据报道是从一个存储设施中被盗走的</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/a-stolen-picasso-just-turned-up-during-a-drug-raid-near-paris-reportedly-taken-from-a-storage-facility-180989010/</link><description>这幅画已被证实，但尚未透露。有报道称这是毕加索为玛丽·泰蕾兹·沃尔特创作的肖像之一</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 20:37:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/a-stolen-picasso-just-turned-up-during-a-drug-raid-near-paris-reportedly-taken-from-a-storage-facility-180989010/</guid></item><item><title>世界上最古老的故事之一《奥德赛》通过人工智能生成的有声读物旁白（由奥斯卡获奖者的语音克隆）获得了现代诠释</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/the-odyssey-one-of-the-worlds-oldest-stories-gets-a-modern-spin-with-ai-generated-audiobook-narration-by-the-voice-clone-of-an-oscar-winner-actor-michael-caine-180989006/</link><description>与此同时，其他参与者正在反对在创意项目中使用人工智能，包括通过新的“人类同意”注册工具</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 18:56:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/the-odyssey-one-of-the-worlds-oldest-stories-gets-a-modern-spin-with-ai-generated-audiobook-narration-by-the-voice-clone-of-an-oscar-winner-actor-michael-caine-180989006/</guid></item><item><title>世界上第一个核时钟正在滴答作响，为研究暗物质和其他物理学之谜开辟了一条新途径</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/the-worlds-first-nuclear-clocks-are-ticking-opening-a-new-way-to-investigate-dark-matter-and-other-mysteries-of-physics-180989002/</link><description>两个独立的科学家团队创造了第一个功能时钟，可以利用放射性元素的原子核来保持超精确的时间</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 16:37:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/the-worlds-first-nuclear-clocks-are-ticking-opening-a-new-way-to-investigate-dark-matter-and-other-mysteries-of-physics-180989002/</guid></item><item><title>这种新发现的蜘蛛构建了一个独特的网，可以将蚂蚁弹射到