.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/female-dolphins-seem-to-remember-which-males-were-aggressive-during-mating-season-and-may-try-to-avoid-them-180988994/</link><description>当研究人员播放咄咄逼人的雄性的水下录音时，有能力怀孕的雌性会游离声音</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jun 2026 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/female-dolphins-seem-to-remember-which-males-were-aggressive-during-mating-season-and-may-try-to-avoid-them-180988994/</guid></item><item><title>科学家可能已经发现了幼发拉底河的起源，它帮助培育了一些最早的已知文明</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/scientists-may-have-discovered-the-origins-of-the-euphrates-river-which-helped-nurture-some-of-the-earliest-known-civilizations-180988966/</link><description>一项新的研究表明，这条著名的水道最初是由两条河流组成的。大约五百万年前的构造活动可能使它们改变路线并合并，从而帮助诞生了新月沃土</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jun 2026 20:51:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/scientists-may-have-discovered-the-origins-of-the-euphrates-river-which-helped-nurture-some-of-the-earliest-known-civilizations-180988966/</guid></item><item><title>鱼类和人类有着惊人相似的睡眠习惯，包括白天小睡</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/fish-and-humans-share-surprisingly-similar-sleep-habits-including-daytime-naps-180988985/</link><description>最近的一项研究表明，斑马鱼有四种睡眠状态，就像人类一样，其中一种类似于下午小睡</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jun 2026 20:35:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/fish-and-humans-share-surprisingly-similar-sleep-habits-including-daytime-naps-180988985/</guid></item></channel></rss>